    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>❗WARNING!❗ Game contains topics and references to mental health and suicide. Players discretion is advised.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Broken Psyche is an episodic horror series unraveling the mystery of your wife's disappearance. Explore the eerie asylum, solve challenging puzzles, and survive the lurking horrors from the monster within while maintaining your sanity.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/62768bf1f402fbcc77d7474365baaaa5.avif?t=1758162397\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras_big/62768bf1f402fbcc77d7474365baaaa5.avif?t=1758162397 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover horrific scenes and tackle the frightening environment</strong> to learn about The Asylum your wife went missing researching. The Asylum is <strong>uncovered in secrets, where decisions here can permanently effect your playthrough</strong>. Broken Psyche rewards explorations, so don't be shy to explore! <strong>Solve puzzles, fight back against the crazy people who occupy here, manage your stress, and find your wife.</strong> Each episode contains <strong>new monsters, puzzles, and more deep lore into the dark stories of Broken Psyche.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/215ea1abcac096812f381f551a7b5d53.poster.avif?t=1758162397\" width=708 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/215ea1abcac096812f381f551a7b5d53.webm?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/564ecd6c6e7377893fa8dee381b46d66.avif?t=1758162397\" width=640 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Managing your stress in Broken Psyche is one of the most important aspects of your journey.</strong> Delve too deep into madness, and your mission to solve the secrets of The Asylum will be vastly more difficult. <strong>Decisions you make could permanently scar or heal your character,</strong> so be wary. Pick me ups like <strong>cigarettes can be a life saver here</strong>, completely destressing any situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/4630fd4d53dc2d110ac507f7e3ae5ccf.poster.avif?t=1758162397\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/4630fd4d53dc2d110ac507f7e3ae5ccf.webm?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/4630fd4d53dc2d110ac507f7e3ae5ccf.mp4?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/0d62e154aad9c91766f50e9839d0229c.poster.avif?t=1758162397\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/0d62e154aad9c91766f50e9839d0229c.webm?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/0d62e154aad9c91766f50e9839d0229c.mp4?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/ee5b09727ca120beed2258e4bfa9ef31.poster.avif?t=1758162397\" width=708 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/ee5b09727ca120beed2258e4bfa9ef31.webm?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/ee5b09727ca120beed2258e4bfa9ef31.mp4?t=1758162397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve too far into the spiral on insanity and pay the consequences. In Broken Psyche you're <strong>battling more than monsters.</strong> You're in an eternal war with your own sanity. It's important <strong>not to make mistakes and take a logical approach to the situations</strong> you will find yourself in. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/f4bdb2f5d758d4262b4548f56ec2a78d.avif?t=1758162397\" width=640 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, there is an economy in Broken Psyche. <strong>Money runs the world, and even more so in The Asylum.</strong> Scavenge and obtain money from any means necessary to trade in valuable materials with The Shopkeeper. <strong>Key items, cigarettes, food, and bonus content can all be obtained through him.</strong> Whether you  find money on a poor deceased soul or in a hidden compartment somewhere, you're <strong>always rewarded for exploring and checking</strong> in corners some may not look themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/19707b9dffdae6a409ad799f2fdaff8b.avif?t=1758162397\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras_big/19707b9dffdae6a409ad799f2fdaff8b.avif?t=1758162397 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/a98d3994525f5f5eafd0a4d6de1abea0.avif?t=1758162397\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras_big/a98d3994525f5f5eafd0a4d6de1abea0.avif?t=1758162397 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>many secrets hidden in the world of Broken Psyche</strong>. A lot of the lore and meanings of The Asylum can be found with <strong>subtle clues and notes scattered around</strong>. Each note with a new face is accompanied by a person kidnapped to The Asylum, and they have a <strong>chilling story to tell.</strong> With clues to be seen about your wife's disappearance, you will need more than the capability to read to figure out where she has gone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040240/extras/87e8255619f9cfc28b5113898e296c2f.avif?t=1758162397\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
